name: Chicken Dodge!
description:
🐔 Chicken Dodge! 🐔 For Nokia Jam 2023!

Press Num 5 or Space to move foreward and release to go backward,

Press Num 2 or Space to restart when you have lost!

Game is also playable with the mouse but it's not recomanded as it's only for mobile users

Only my 3th Jam ever and 1st here!

Coding: MinosDio

Music: BlookyTune
